=CONCATENATE(MID(A3,(FIND(",",A3,1)+2),8),".",MID(A3,1,(FIND(",",A3,1)-1)),"@email.com")

Smith,John ==> John.Smith@email.com

Psuedocode: Concatenate string A + "." + string B + "@email.com"
- Where string A is first name, or all characters AFTER the comma
- Where string B is the last name, or all characters BEFORE the comma
